thon\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (bins - item) ** 2\n```\n\n### Implementation 9: Logarithmic Fit Heuristic\nApplies a logarithmic transformation to the remaining space.\n\n```python\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return np.log(bins - item + 1)\n```\n\n### Implementation 10: Trigonometric Fit Heuristic\nUses a trigonometric function to compute the priority.\n\n```python\ndef priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return np.sin(bins - item) + np.cos(item)\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return np.exp(item - bins) * (item * np.mean(bins)) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 8\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.min(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 6 + np.cos(np.pi * (item + bins)) * 1\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.max(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 5 + np.cos(np.pi * (item - bins)) * 2\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.mean(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 7 + np.cos(np.pi * (item - bins)) * 3\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.mean(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 9 + np.cos(np.pi * (item - bins)) * 4\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.mean(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 10 + np.cos(np.pi * (item - bins)) * 5\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.mean(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.sin(np.pi * (item / bins)) * 12 + np.cos(np.pi * (item - bins)) * 6\n', 'def priority(item: float, bins: np.ndarray) -> np.ndarray:\n    return (item * np.mean(bins)) * np.exp(item - bins) + np.s